episodes.title: Scary truth of Cult Initiation: My journey from cultism to freedom
episodes.description: In this deeply personal video, I share my harrowing experience with cultism and the incredible journey I undertook to break free. Join me as I reveal the hidden dangers of cults, the psychological traps they set, and how I found the strength to reclaim my life. This is a story of resilience, hope, and the power of self-discovery. If you're struggling or know someone who is, this video offers insight, support, and a message of empowerment. Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe for more real-life stories and discussions."
